DTSTART:20260325T020000Z
DESCRIPTION:This is Jeopardy! Get ready for an epic trivia experience like 
	no other with Jeopardy! Bar League. Geeks Who Drink is partnering with Son
	y Pictures Television and bringing America's Favorite Quiz Show® out of th
	e studio and straight to your local bar. No more shouting at your TV: with
	 Jeopardy! Bar League you get a thrilling\, team-based experience with rea
	l clues from the Jeopardy! writers' room\, all on your phone. Gather your 
	smartest \\(or most entertaining\\) friends\, form your team\, and head to
	 Sodam Chicken in Shoreline for Jeopardy! Bar League on the 2nd and 4th Tu
	esday of the month at 7pm.\n\nTo learn more\, visit jeopardybarleague.com.
	\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/jeopardy-bar-league-at-s
