UID:yZg-IMGWq3zGtvQxeF3SF
SUMMARY:Family Business Exchange | Webinar
DTSTAMP:20260318T065004Z
DTSTART:20260326T190000Z
DESCRIPTION:Save the Date!\n\nAbout the Family Business Exchange\n\nSeattle
	 University’s Family Business Exchange \\(FBX\\) is a community of Pacific
	 Northwest family business owners who gather to engage in education\, netw
	orking\, and professional development tailored specifically to their needs
	.\n\nFBX provides opportunities for families to address their unique chall
	enges through relevant programming. It serves as a forum for information e
	xchange with the goal of helping each member thrive through future generat
	ions. Areas of best practice that we cover include family business success
	ion planning\, governance\, leadership development and growth\, among othe
	rs.\n\nAbout Assured Partners\n\nAssured Partners is a Seattle-based insur
	ance brokerage that provides tailored commercial insurance\, employee bene
	fits\, risk management and personal insurance solutions to businesses and 
	individuals\, drawing on the expertise of a national partnership of indepe
	ndent brokers. Please contact Nick Brewe to connect with Assured Partners 
	about your business insurance needs.\n\n \n\nThis event is open to FBX mem
	bers and prospective members.\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/det
	ails/family-business-exchange-webinar/18260248/2026-03-26T00\n\nFrom SEAto
	day - All Events
URL:https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/family-business-exchange-
	webinar/18260248/2026-03-26T00
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:seatoday-all
CATEGORIES:SEAtoday - All Events
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT1H
END:VEVENT
